\" aria-label=\"Tìm kiếm\" class=\"p-2.5 rounded-lg text-[#475569] hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors\"><svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z\"></path></svg></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"bg-[#EC1313] text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold hover:bg-[#d41111] transition-all hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-red-200 duration-300\">Ứng tuyển ngay</button></div><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Mở menu điều hướng\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"mobile-navigation\" class=\"md:hidden p-2 rounded-lg text-[#475569] hover:bg-slate-100\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></header><main class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"bg-white\"><section class=\"relative min-h-[400px] lg:min-h-[500px] flex items-center overflow-hidden bg-[#0F172A]\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#EC1313]/15 via-transparent to-[#0F172A]\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-20 right-20 w-72 h-72 bg-[#EC1313]/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-10 left-10 w-56 h-56 bg-[#EC1313]/5 rounded-full blur-2xl pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 w-full\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full mb-8 border border-white/20\"><div class=\"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#EC1313] animate-pulse\"></div><span class=\"text-white/90 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase\">Lĩnh vực hoạt động</span></div><h1 class=\"text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-black text-white leading-[1.05] mb-6 tracking-tight\">Lĩnh vực<!-- --> <span class=\"text-[#EC1313]\">&amp; Dịch vụ</span></h1><p class=\"text-lg lg:text-xl text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-xl\">Chúng tôi cung cấp các giải pháp toàn diện cho chuỗi giá trị thương mại điện tử hiện đại, từ nền tảng bán hàng đến logistics và thanh toán.</p><button type=\"button\" class=\"group bg-[#EC1313] text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-[#d41111] transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-red-500/30 flex items-center gap-3\">Liên hệ tư vấn<svg class=\"w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3\"></path></svg></button></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 lg:py-28 bg-[#FAFAFA]\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[rgba(236,19,19,0.08)] px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-4\"><span class=\"text-[#EC1313] text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase\">Dịch vụ nổi bật</span></div><h2 class=\"text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-black text-[#0F172A] mb-4 tracking-tight\">CÁC DỊCH VỤ CỦA CHÚNG TÔI</h2><p class=\"text-[#475569] text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Khám phá hệ sinh thái giải pháp công nghệ toàn diện cho doanh nghiệp của bạn</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 mb-12\"><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"true\" class=\"px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full font-semibold text-sm transition-all duration-300 bg-[#EC1313] text-white shadow-lg shadow-red-200\">Tất cả</button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full font-semibold text-sm transition-all duration-300 bg-white text-[#475569] border border-slate-200 hover:border-[#EC1313]/30 hover:text-[#EC1313]\">Thương mại điện tử</button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full font-semibold text-sm transition-all duration-300 bg-white text-[#475569] border border-slate-200 hover:border-[#EC1313]/30 hover:text-[#EC1313]\">Logistics</button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full font-semibold text-sm transition-all duration-300 bg-white text-[#475569] border border-slate-200 hover:border-[#EC1313]/30 hover:text-[#EC1313]\">Thanh toán</button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full font-semibold text-sm transition-all duration-300 bg-white text-[#475569] border border-slate-200 hover:border-[#EC1313]/30 hover:text-[#EC1313]\">Dữ liệu &amp; AI</button></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"group relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden cursor-pointer shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 bg-white border border-slate-100\" aria-label=\"Xem chi tiết dịch vụ Nền tảng TMĐT Đa kênh\"><div class=\"aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"/images/sinh-nhat-outdoor.webp\" alt=\"Nền tảng TMĐT Đa kênh\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#0F172A]/90 via-[#0F172A]/30 to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-4 left-4\"><span class=\"inline-block bg-[#EC1313] text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider\">Thương mại điện tử</span></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-bold text-lg mb-1 group-hover:text-[#EC1313] transition-colors\">Nền tảng TMĐT Đa kênh</h3><p class=\"text-white/85 text-sm leading-relaxed line-clamp-2\">Xây dựng hệ thống kinh doanh trực tuyến đa nền tảng: Website, Mobile App, tích hợp sàn TMĐT.</p><div class=\"mt-3 flex items-center gap-2 text-white/80 text-sm group-hover:text-[#EC1313] transition-colors\"><span>Xem chi tiết</span><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-0.5 bg-[#EC1313] w-0 group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-500\"></div></div></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"group relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden cursor-pointer shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 bg-white border border-slate-100\" aria-label=\"Xem chi tiết dịch vụ Hệ thống Logistics 4.0\"><div class=\"aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"/images/c2ccbf1858e405f5122d22037e50428c8430c63f.webp\" alt=\"Hệ thống Logistics 4.0\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#0F172A]/90 via-[#0F172A]/30 to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-4 left-4\"><span class=\"inline-block bg-[#EC1313] text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider\">Logistics</span></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-bold text-lg mb-1 group-hover:text-[#EC1313] transition-colors\">Hệ thống Logistics 4.0</h3><p class=\"text-white/85 text-sm leading-relaxed line-clamp-2\">Vận hành thông minh, giao hàng tốc độ cao trên toàn quốc với công nghệ quản lý chuỗi cung ứng hiện đại.</p><div class=\"mt-3 flex items-center gap-2 text-white/80 text-sm group-hover:text-[#EC1313] transition-colors\"><span>Xem chi tiết</span><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-0.5 bg-[#EC1313] w-0 group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-500\"></div></div></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"group relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden cursor-pointer shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 bg-white border border-slate-100\" aria-label=\"Xem chi tiết dịch vụ Giải pháp Thanh toán Số\"><div class=\"aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"/images/sinh-nhat-quy4-2.webp\" alt=\"Giải pháp Thanh toán Số\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#0F172A]/90 via-[#0F172A]/30 to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-4 left-4\"><span class=\"inline-block bg-[#EC1313] text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider\">Thanh toán</span></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-bold text-lg mb-1 group-hover:text-[#EC1313] transition-colors\">Giải pháp Thanh toán Số</h3><p class=\"text-white/85 text-sm leading-relaxed line-clamp-2\">Hệ thống thanh toán tích hợp đa phương thức: ví điện tử, thẻ, mã QR, hỗ trợ mua trước trả sau.</p><div class=\"mt-3 flex items-center gap-2 text-white/80 text-sm group-hover:text-[#EC1313] transition-colors\"><span>Xem chi tiết</span><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-0.5 bg-[#EC1313] w-0 group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-500\"></div></div></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"group relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden cursor-pointer shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 bg-white border border-slate-100\" aria-label=\"Xem chi tiết dịch vụ Phân tích dữ liệu Big Data\"><div class=\"aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"/images/vinh-danh-top3.webp\" alt=\"Phân tích dữ liệu Big Data\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#0F172A]/90 via-[#0F172A]/30 to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-4 left-4\"><span class=\"inline-block bg-[#EC1313] text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider\">Dữ liệu &amp; AI</span></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-bold text-lg mb-1 group-hover:text-[#EC1313] transition-colors\">Phân tích dữ liệu Big Data</h3><p class=\"text-white/85 text-sm leading-relaxed line-clamp-2\">Thu thập và phân tích hành vi người dùng, tối ưu chiến lược kinh doanh qua dữ liệu thực chiến.</p><div class=\"mt-3 flex items-center gap-2 text-white/80 text-sm group-hover:text-[#EC1313] transition-colors\"><span>Xem chi tiết</span><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-0.5 bg-[#EC1313] w-0 group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-500\"></div></div></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"group relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden cursor-pointer shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 bg-white border border-slate-100\" aria-label=\"Xem chi tiết dịch vụ Giám định &amp; Chứng nhận\"><div class=\"aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"/images/sinh-nhat-outdoor.webp\" alt=\"Giám định &amp; Chứng nhận\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#0F172A]/90 via-[#0F172A]/30 to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-4 left-4\"><span class=\"inline-block bg-[#EC1313] text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider\">Thương mại điện tử</span></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-bold text-lg mb-1 group-hover:text-[#EC1313] transition-colors\">Giám định &amp; Chứng nhận</h3><p class=\"text-white/85 text-sm leading-relaxed line-clamp-2\">Dịch vụ giám định sản phẩm, chứng nhận hợp quy theo tiêu chuẩn Việt Nam và quốc tế.</p><div class=\"mt-3 flex items-center gap-2 text-white/80 text-sm group-hover:text-[#EC1313] transition-colors\"><span>Xem chi tiết</span><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-0.5 bg-[#EC1313] w-0 group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-500\"></div></div></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"group relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden cursor-pointer shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 bg-white border border-slate-100\" aria-label=\"Xem chi tiết dịch vụ Tư vấn Chuyển đổi số\"><div class=\"aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"/images/vinh-danh-top3.webp\" alt=\"Tư vấn Chuyển đổi số\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#0F172A]/90 via-[#0F172A]/30 to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-4 left-4\"><span class=\"inline-block bg-[#EC1313] text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider\">Dữ liệu &amp; AI</span></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-bold text-lg mb-1 group-hover:text-[#EC1313] transition-colors\">Tư vấn Chuyển đổi số</h3><p class=\"text-white/85 text-sm leading-relaxed line-clamp-2\">Đồng hành cùng doanh nghiệp trong hành trình chuyển đổi số toàn diện từ quy trình đến công nghệ.</p><div class=\"mt-3 flex items-center gap-2 text-white/80 text-sm group-hover:text-[#EC1313] transition-colors\"><span>Xem chi tiết</span><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-0.5 bg-[#EC1313] w-0 group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-500\"></div></div></button></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 lg:py-28 bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[rgba(236,19,19,0.08)] px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-4\"><span class=\"text-[#EC1313] text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase\">Sản phẩm</span></div><h2 class=\"text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-black text-[#0F172A] mb-4 tracking-tight\">HỆ SINH THÁI SẢN PHẨM BYD</h2><p class=\"text-[#64748B] text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Bộ giải pháp công nghệ tích hợp, đáp ứng mọi nhu cầu kinh doanh số</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6\"><div class=\"group bg-[#FAFAFA] rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-[#EC1313]/20 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 text-center\"><div class=\"w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-2xl bg-[#EC1313]/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[#EC1313] group-hover:bg-[#EC1313] group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300\"><svg class=\"w-8 h-8\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" d=\"M13.5 21v-7.5a.75.75 0 01.75-.75h3a.75.75 0 01.75.75V21m-4.5 0H2.36m11.14 0H18m0 0h3.64m-1.39 0V9.349m-16.5 11.65V9.35m0 0a3.001 3.001 0 003.75-.615A2.993 2.993 0 009.75 9.75c.896 0 1.7-.393 2.25-1.016a2.993 2.993 0 002.25 1.016c.896 0 1.7-.393 2.25-1.016a3.001 3.001 0 003.75.614m-16.5 0a3.004 3.004 0 01-.621-4.72L4.318 3.44A1.5 1.5 0 015.378 3h13.243a1.5 1.5 0 011.06.